text: Miguel Murillo (born September 29, 1993) is a Costa Rican judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 73 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Shohei Ono. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Costa Rican male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Costa Rica Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
